   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"04t.html\">一覧　（タ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.co.jp/exec/obidos/redirect?link_code=ur2&amp;tag=click20thcetu-22&amp;camp=247&amp;creative=1211&amp;path=external-search%3Fsearch-type=ss%26index=books-jp%26keyword=%25E5%2586%2586%25E8%25B0%25B7%2520%25E8%258B%25B1%25E4%25BA%258C\" target=\"_blank\">本を入手</a><img src=\"http://www.assoc-amazon.jp/e/ir?t=click20thcetu-22&amp;l=ur2&amp;o=9\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:none !important; margin:0px !important;\"></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　福島県出身。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　小笠原プロなどを経てＪ・Ｏスタジオ入社、日独合作映画「新しき土」を担当。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　東宝に入社し、特殊技術課を創設。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦後、大映で「虹男」「透明人間現わる」などの特撮を手がける。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　東宝復帰後、日本初の怪獣ＳＦ映画「ゴジラ」で日本映画技術賞を受賞。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　円谷特技プロを発足、「ウルトラマン」など特撮テレビ映画で怪獣ブームを巻き起こす。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
